ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Eastern Portion of the South Slave Region) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (EASTERN PORTION OF THE SOUTH SLAVE REGION) ORDER which withdraws from disposal the surface and subsurface rights to certain lands, for a period of three years, in order to facilitate the conclusion of Aboriginal land agreements.
